\begin_inset Formula $M\in\reals^{n\times n}$
\end_inset

 be a psd matrix.
 By the spectral theorem, we can write 
\begin_inset Formula $M=Q\Sigma Q^{T}$
\end_inset

.
 Then by the argument above, 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\diag(Q^{T}MQ)=\diag(\Sigma)\succeq0.
\]

\end_inset


